{"about_the_game":"&quot;Bopp Files&quot; is a spot-the-difference game that combines the elements of room escape, similar to &quot;Exit No.8&quot;. In 1998, you wake up from the apartment with a loss of memory. A demon who claims to be an &quot;Exile&quot; blocks your apartment, demanding you to escape within the stipulated time, otherwise, you will face certain death. But will the demon really keep his promise? What is the demon's purpose after all?<br><br>All of this stems from the meteorite fragments left on Earth by the Hale-Bopp Comet.<br><br>Players play as Benjamin Cooper to experience the entire event he went through.<br>[img{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/2024-07-02_21-01-45_x2642024741029191.gif][/img]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game features:</h2><br>1.Find and discover abnormal spaces in the loop space.<br>2.Explore the diaries of Benjamin Cooper and a cult bishop to find the conditions to defeat the demon.<br>3.Reveal the true purpose of the demon, and experience the highly aggressive atmosphere brought by the narrative tricks the demon uses in this gamble.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3016610/extras/2024-07-02_21-01-45_x2642024741034383.gif?t=1732196293\" /><br><br>Producer\uff1a\u963f\u9e7f\u7684alu<br>Distributo\uff1a\u7cd5\u85af\u79d1\u6280<br>Promotion Assistance::\u98ce\u57df\u6e38\u620f","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Gamble","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3016610/67309a77cd6994ff22db7cebc37300d485e0d37b.jpg"},{"name":"Deception","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3016610/ac2cf1c09428b110e1d23855d10b1295e713edd6.jpg"},{"name":"Forgotten","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3016610/21491cd729fe1fd743d404cdf59822d0a6f773c7.jpg"},{"name":"Strategy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3016610/e120b299791269e11357253173b